data.description:
Really nice 4 bedroom, 2 bath brick home, large corner lot, circle driveway, with a great shop!!  Great family home or a wonderful home to retire and enjoy the peace and quiet!  This home has a living area with fireplace open with the dining area, and a large den family room!!  The kitchen has a wall of pretty farmhouse pantry cabinets allowing plenty of storage. Master suite is large with coffered ceiling, double vanity bath, separate shower and the master bedroom has a large walk-in closet.  The guest bath is a jack and jill accommodating 3 bedrooms and visitors.  The home has a walk-through utility room that leads to the garage.   The back yard oasis has a covered patio with misters and roll down shades, an open patio area with an outdoor kitchen area complete with a bar, bbq grill, small fridge.  Enjoy some cool drinks in the gazebo overlooking the inground pool with a cute frog fountain!   
The shop is totally almost the best feature of the property.  Approximately 1320 sq. ft. with two large roll up doors, a walk door, and a lift for auto work.  The shop has electrical to accommodate most equipment, water, concrete floors and is ready for the handyman, auto work, do it yourselfer!   Also has a small She -shed on a concrete slab, great for storage or golf cart.  Slab beside the she-shed is large enough for RV parking (doesn't have a cover, but you can add one!).  
This property has a whole house water filter system, tank less water heater, and has been well maintained.  So much to offer and it is already there for you to enjoy!  Close proximity to Copperas Cove, Lampasas, Killeen!  Must see this one before it is SOLD!!
